{"tid":1072860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港U23鬥新加坡發生多次衝突 外流球員徐宏傑遭新加坡球員揮拳襲擊背部","createTime":"2019-03-22T09:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T10:20:07.000Z","uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29f1a31433988161d25f7d7eb4d3d6af760714f7","tid":1072860,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T09:37:34.000Z","msg":"U23亞洲足球錦標賽外圍賽於蒙古烏蘭巴托舉行。<br />\n<br />\n香港對新加坡全場賽事，新加坡都有不少小動作，新加坡球員亦開始偶爾以言語挑釁港隊球員，到下半場初段起，兩軍不斷出現零星衝突，甚至完場後兩軍握手亦爆口角，令氣氛一度緊張。<br />\n<br />\n徐宏傑賽後解釋，新加坡球員在今仗任何時候都很多小動作：「賽後握手時經過，後背也被打了一槌，是認真地打，就更加躁。」已在中甲效力逾一季的「傑仔」坦言，在中甲也未見這種情況，但認為更大原因是球證未能及時控制：「這些動作，無論場內場外，球證正常也一定見到，有少許覺得是球證執法的問題，導致這情況。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2582236/org/00caa52e18aaf27c3e0bccab6f14338d.jpg/PygQoR3u6x3IcKy2FuedxZPeKAwDwlx-CPgcogj4HKI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2582236%2Forg%2F00caa52e18aaf27c3e0bccab6f14338d.jpg%2FPygQoR3u6x3IcKy2FuedxZPeKAwDwlx-CPgcogj4HKI&h=fd2fdce9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2582463/org/c3d289085dfeb961876d0aa8ca792a8a.jpg/qRTrcag8ZJv7dlBCgqW4BYPFh7U4pjmTP8UmAhXFJgI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2582463%2Forg%2Fc3d289085dfeb961876d0aa8ca792a8a.jpg%2FqRTrcag8ZJv7dlBCgqW4BYPFh7U4pjmTP8UmAhXFJgI&h=46b437e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a891946ef66231d4f54bf5f3ae423320f52fee3","tid":1072860,"uid":135522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:05:34.000Z","msg":"「傑仔」坦言，在中甲也未見這種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6821a36965870bd766d0e8d9f7ce6496a3fcabdc","tid":1072860,"uid":39226,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T10:20:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾坡狗"}]}